Ikipe nkuru y'igihugu cy'u [[Rwanda]]<nowiki/>mu marushanwa mpuzamahanga ya ruhago, iri mu nshingano za Federasiyo y'umupira w'amaguru mu Rwanda kandi ikaba imwe mu zigize Federasiyo Nyafurika y'umpira w'amaguru muri Afrika. Amavubi ahanini yitoreza muri stade Amahoro iherereye i Kigali, mu murwa mukuru w' u Rwanda. 

== Amateka ==
Amavubi yitabiriye bwa mbere amarushanwa y'igikombe Nyafurika cya ruhago muri 2004 .<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/3438195.stm|title=Rwanda's football mercenaries|website=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=28 January 2004|access-date=18 January 2013}}</ref> . Umukino wa mbere Amavubi yaguye miswi na Guinea <ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/3433831.stm|title=Rwanda snatch dramatic point|website=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=28 January 2004|access-date=18 January 2013}}</ref> igitego kimwe kuri kimwe, nyuma yaje gutsindwa na Tunisia ibitego bibiri kuri kimwe, ndetse itsinda Repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya Congo igitego kimwe ku busa. Nyamara ibyo ntibyari bihagije ngo u Rwanda rukomeze kuko rwaje gusezererwa<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/3448083.stm|title=Rwanda dumped out|website=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=31 January 2004|access-date=18 January 2013}}</ref>.

== Amazina ==
Mu mikino ya FIFA u Rwanda rugaragazwa n'ijambo: "'''RWA".''' Iri jambo rikoreshwa kandi na [[FIFA]],  [[Confederation of African Football|CAF]] ndetse na [[Council for East and Central Africa Football Associations|CECAFA]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/associations/association=rwa/countryInfo.html|title=Member Association&nbsp;– Rwanda|website=FIFA.com|publisher=FIFA|access-date=19 June 2016}}</ref> U Rwanda rwakunzwe kurangwa kandi n'ijambo: "'''RR'''," bisobanuye, ''Repubulika y'u Rwanda'' cyangwa ''République du Rwanda mu'' rurimi rw'igifaransa.

